{"tid":1927120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開] 我想開打一條新條新戰線 轉守為攻 劍指9月立法會選舉","createTime":"2020-03-15T14:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T13:16:06.000Z","uid":63639,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"81d521593d312c07baba44517a7cc099ac382073","tid":1927120,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我今日開過一個post 但可能我表達太差 推唔到個post<br />\n所以依家重開一個 想同大家講一講我既諗法<br />\n<br />\n转守为攻 成立中国香港义和团 刻不容缓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926447</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n由6月以來 雖然不停有抗爭 但不得不承認大部分時候<br />\n我地都只係以一個防禦既方式去抵抗港共既侵蝕 <br />\n真正有傷害既攻擊只有黃色經濟圈同國際戰線 但成效都未顯得好大<br />\n<br />\n同時 我又係到諗 我地成日捉鬼 又擔心畀人統戰 所以我突發奇想 <br />\n點解我地唔可以做相同嘅野呢？<br />\n現實上有組織力既組織都係有名氣既團體/政黨 要組織我既計劃同諗法<br />\n只可以依靠群眾自我組織<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c577e83d62e62edb8784ca146d498955e3ffc0b","tid":1927120,"uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"請大家幫手推一推"},{"pid":"c4ca213dde9e7a98ba78ccf1f9699cee72b91621","tid":1927120,"uid":104819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60f9888a9c1946adc5572514a28a3de2e1e3a1c6","tid":1927120,"uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"請大家幫手推一推"},{"pid":"1c107f3f59000dd9624416e779adbaaa4810949d","tid":1927120,"uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"請大家幫手推一推"},{"pid":"11754ad5b57670852a83759ed6381e94adc31455","tid":1927120,"uid":91397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca885bfab350616d8fbe353903af45bf3bb3dd9f","tid":1927120,"uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:46:03.0